snippet.title: Geri Greviews
snippet.description:
I'm an artist in many ways.
I do lots of types of art, like drawing, different kinds of visual design, dancing, singing, sculpting, and even cooking and a bit of cosplay.
I'm also practicing natural bodybuilding, for self-development and peek health.
But my main focus and passion is to express myself through video creating
YouTuber/Streamer that makes:
Warhammer
Movie Reviews,
TV Show Reviews,
Trailer Reactions/breakdowns,
Gaming Streams and first impression videos.
Gaming Reviews,
Fitness and Health videos and
Travel Vlogs.
